author: rhillegas
msg: Checkin patch to DERBY-955 which uses Sed to mask out jdk1.6-specific test diffs introduced by the JDBC4 subclasses of SQLException. This eliminates a number of jdk1.6-specific canons.

author: djd
msg: DERBY-1158 (partial) Implement downgrading a request to create any holdable statement in a global
transaction to return a non-holdable statement. Such a downgrade adds a SQLWarning to the Connection
object. This follows section 16.1.3.1 from JDBC 4.0 proposed final draft.
